Package: AutoRNAseq
Title: An R Package for Automated End-to-End RNA-Seq Analysis and Biomarker Discovery
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Muhammad", "Haris", , "mharis.202101862@gcuf.edu.pk", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = ""))
Description: AutoRNAseq v1 provides a Shiny web application for 
    interactive and reproducible RNA-Seq differential gene expression analysis,
    downstream functional enrichment (GO, KEGG, GSEA), protein-protein 
    interaction (PPI) network analysis, and machine-learning-based biomarker 
    discovery. Built on the Shiny framework with Bioconductor packages.
